Run system diagnostics

Usage: wheelctl diag test [OPTIONS] [TEST_TYPE]

Arguments:
  [TEST_TYPE]  Test type [possible values: motor, encoder, usb, thermal, all]

Options:
  -d, --device <DEVICE>  Device ID or name
      --json             Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -v, --verbose...       Verbose logging
  -h, --help             Print help
